column5: Was better than average yeah lots of slots & trophy's. Jig and Minnie 11-12 for. 18 were tough to find, weather was Canada cold one day warn the next. House owner was laying new tules made less than enjoyable trip othe than fish 28 w 38 jack two largest!
Curious what area of the east end you fished. Thanks, PjShorthorn

Lac seul fishing the past 7 days. Fishing has been good, at times great. Fish are still shallow, off the rocks and in the mud, more or less everywhere we stopped. We fish all artificial, cranks/jerks and jig/twister. Went up north west of Taylor’s island today. Lots of slots, some big ones, overall good fishing. Dodged a rainstorm and came off early, otherwise we’d still be out there. Been coming up here since 1991, I was 11 then, now my own kids are learning the waters. Passing the tradition on that my grandfather started in the early 1960’s🤙🏻
